<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:06:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>为什么这位以色列艺术家不会参加她在南非的新展览</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-artist-has-a-new-exhibition-in-south-africa-she-wont-be-attending/0000018d-5b13-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fe5b30000</link><description>以色列艺术家莫兰·克利格 (Moran Kliger) 原定飞往开普敦参加她的展览开幕式，但 10 月 7 日的袭击、加沙持续的战争以及海牙审判造成的以色列和南非之间的敌意让她感到出发不安全</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:46:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-artist-has-a-new-exhibition-in-south-africa-she-wont-be-attending/0000018d-5b13-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fe5b30000</guid></item><item><title>纸上的恐怖：以色列人于 10 月 7 日设计出迷人的海报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/horror-on-paper-israeli-designers-made-captivating-posters-on-october-7/0000018d-5f13-d0af-a3af-7fbf4e210000</link><description>一个关于哈马斯袭击的展览将有 70 张海报印在 70 x 70 厘米的纸上，分为七个类别</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:22:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/horror-on-paper-israeli-designers-made-captivating-posters-on-october-7/0000018d-5f13-d0af-a3af-7fbf4e210000</guid></item><item><title>“我的教室用品是一块橡皮和一把 AK-47”：以色列顶级讽刺节目嘲笑近东救济工程处</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/my-classroom-supplies-are-an-eraser-and-an-ak-47-top-israeli-satire-show-mocks-unrwa/0000018d-5f39-d4f8-a9df-5f3dd12b0000</link><description>以色列最受欢迎的喜剧小品节目《Eretz Nehederet》在最近 10 月 7 日发生与哈马斯有关联的指控后嘲笑了近东救济工程处。其中还有一位虚构的联合国秘书长，他对近东救济工程处感到震惊，他说，“当然，我认为我们需要将他们的资金增加一倍”</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 12:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/my-classroom-supplies-are-an-eraser-and-an-ak-47-top-israeli-satire-show-mocks-unrwa/0000018d-5f39-d4f8-a9df-5f3dd12b0000</guid></item><item><title>她儿时的大屠杀梦想使这位以色列电影制片人一路登上了奥斯卡奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-animator-hoping-to-become-the-first-israeli-woman-to-win-an-oscar/0000018d-5b7d-de55-a99d-ff7fcfc10000</link><description>塔尔·坎特 (Tal Kantor) 希望十月份访问好莱坞宣传她的动画短片《给猪的信》，但加沙战争改变了一切，包括人们对她获得奥斯卡提名的感人作品的反应，该作品讲述了大屠杀幸存者以及同情心和同情心的力量。共情</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-animator-hoping-to-become-the-first-israeli-woman-to-win-an-oscar/0000018d-5b7d-de55-a99d-ff7fcfc10000</guid></item><item><title>挪威敦促维持近东救济工程处的资金，表示没有收到以色列关于指控的通报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/norway-urges-maintaining-unrwa-funding-says-it-wasnt-briefed-by-israel-on-allegations/0000018d-5eef-d4f8-a9df-5fef0bbe0000</link><description>这个斯堪的纳维亚国家敦促近东救济工程处的其他捐助国“反思更广泛的后果”，因为有报道称其员工参与了哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织 10 月 7 日的袭击，因此削减了资金。挪威外交部长表示，近东救济工程处是加沙 150 万难民的重要生命线</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/norway-urges-maintaining-unrwa-funding-says-it-wasnt-briefed-by-israel-on-allegations/0000018d-5eef-d4f8-a9df-5fef0bbe0000</guid></item><item><title>唱片公司因反以色列言论而终止与罗杰·沃特斯的合同</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/record-company-cuts-contract-with-roger-waters-amid-history-of-anti-israel-statements/0000018d-5ecf-d0fc-a9bd-5edf3f6a0000</link><description>《综艺》杂志网站报道称，这家德国公司此举也是继平克·弗洛伊德乐队创始人过去针对以色列、美国以及支持俄罗斯总统普京的言论之后做出的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/record-company-cuts-contract-with-roger-waters-amid-history-of-anti-israel-statements/0000018d-5ecf-d0fc-a9bd-5edf3f6a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了周二在加沙地带战斗中丧生的三名预备役军人的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/israeli-army-names-three-reservists-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018d-5e49-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d93a00000</link><description>军方还表示，周二有五名士兵在加沙的战斗中受重伤。他们正在接受治疗，并已通知家人</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 07:53:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/israeli-army-names-three-reservists-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018d-5e49-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d93a00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的前幕僚长将阿里·哈罗 (Ari Harow) 被判犯有欺诈和违反信任罪的国家证据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ex-chief-of-staff-ari-harow-convicted-of-fraud-breach-of-trust/0000018d-5e72-d0af-a3af-7efea9360000</link><description>哈罗被指控从一家他保留所有权的公司获取利润，尽管他在上任前被勒令出售自己的部分</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 07:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ex-chief-of-staff-ari-harow-convicted-of-fraud-breach-of-trust/0000018d-5e72-d0af-a3af-7efea9360000</guid></item><item><title>被认为是哈马斯在加沙囚禁的以色列警察于 10 月 7 日被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-thought-to-be-hamas-hostage-in-gaza-was-killed-on-october-7/0000018d-5e20-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d20b30000</link><description>吉利是10月7日遇害的61名警察之一。吉利是以色列南部梅塔尔的居民，10月7日正在休病假，当他了解到发生紧急情况时，他决定前往内盖夫西部</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 07:02:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-thought-to-be-hamas-hostage-in-gaza-was-killed-on-october-7/0000018d-5e20-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d20b30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡目前的联盟将无法在与哈马斯的人质协议中幸存</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-is-doomed-whether-israel-agrees-to-a-hostage-deal-or-not/0000018d-5bde-d0fc-a9bd-5fdf39740000</link><description>以色列总理正接近一个关键的决策点：要么在做出重大让步的情况下接受该协议并面临许多以色列人的批评，要么按照极右翼部长本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇的要求拒绝该协议，从而冒着中间派部长离开的风险。与此同时，他采取了含糊的半否认态度</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 04:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-is-doomed-whether-israel-agrees-to-a-hostage-deal-or-not/0000018d-5bde-d0fc-a9bd-5fdf39740000</guid></item><item><title>没有人相信卡汉主义者空洞地威胁要推翻内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/nobody-believes-the-kahanists-empty-threats-to-topple-the-israeli-government/0000018d-5c1e-d4f8-a9df-5f3ef2680000</link><description>鉴于他们没有参与战争的管理，驱逐加沙巴勒斯坦人的支持者们一直与甘茨的中间派政党发生冲突 — — 主要是因为该党在民意调查中的支持率飙升。即使本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇反对人质交易，他们也不会走完整九码</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/nobody-believes-the-kahanists-empty-threats-to-topple-the-israeli-government/0000018d-5c1e-d4f8-a9df-5f3ef2680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击叙利亚目标；哈马斯“研究”加沙人质协议提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-live/israeli-army-admits-its-flooding-hamas-tunnels-in-gaza-in-bid-to-destroy-them/0000018d-5d82-d4f8-a9df-5faea22c0000</link><description>报告：潜在的人质协议包括在为期六周的停火期间释放所有以色列平民人质 ■ 以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的三名预备役士兵的名字 半岛电视台发布了以色列士兵在杰宁医院突袭中伪装的以色列士兵的镜头 ■ 以色列国防军称袭击了医院叙利亚军队连夜岗哨，以应对戈兰高地的火箭袭击 ■ 以色列国防军称袭击了黎巴嫩目标 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部称，迄今为止已有 26,900 名巴勒斯坦人丧生</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 03:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-live/israeli-army-admits-its-flooding-hamas-tunnels-in-gaza-in-bid-to-destroy-them/0000018d-5d82-d4f8-a9df-5faea22c0000</guid></item><item><title>“这又发生了”：10 月 7 日失去家人的大屠杀幸存者在议会发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/its-happening-again-holocaust-survivors-who-lost-family-october-7-speak-at-knesset/0000018d-5be6-d4f8-a9df-5feef9620000</link><description>当哈马斯对以色列社区发动残酷袭击时，1,894 名大屠杀幸存者（其中 554 名来自加沙边境附近社区）被撤离家园</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 00:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/its-happening-again-holocaust-survivors-who-lost-family-october-7-speak-at-knesset/0000018d-5be6-d4f8-a9df-5feef9620000</guid></item><item><title>死亡与捐款：处理 10 月 7 日死者的以色列志愿者组织是否利用了自己的作用？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/death-and-donations-did-the-volunteer-group-handling-the-october-7-dead-exploit-its-role/0000018d-5a73-d997-adff-df7bdb670000</link><description>哈马斯袭击发生后，扎卡志愿者组织立即开始在以色列南部遭到破坏的社区收集尸体，而以色列国防军则让士兵们在一旁接受搜寻遗体的训练。一项调查揭露了疏忽、错误信息和利用死者作为道具的筹款活动的案例</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/death-and-donations-did-the-volunteer-group-handling-the-october-7-dead-exploit-its-role/0000018d-5a73-d997-adff-df7bdb670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会将投票表决驱逐支持国际法院种族灭绝案的议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-knesset-to-vote-on-expelling-lawmaker-over-support-for-icj-genocide-case/0000018d-5be2-d0fc-a9bd-5fff647f0000</link><description>奥弗·卡西夫否认了他支持哈马斯针对以色列的武装斗争的说法，并补充说针对他的弹劾程序是政治迫害</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-knesset-to-vote-on-expelling-lawmaker-over-support-for-icj-genocide-case/0000018d-5be2-d0fc-a9bd-5fff647f0000</guid></item><item><title>战争已经过去一百多天了，议会仍然没有发挥作用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/over-a-hundred-days-into-the-war-and-the-knesset-still-isnt-functioning/0000018d-5bf2-d0af-a3af-7bfed7db0000</link><description>自10月7日战争爆发以来，以色列议会创下新低，走廊空荡荡，活动非常有限。 “MK们已经不再来了，因为什么也没发生”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 20:58:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/over-a-hundred-days-into-the-war-and-the-knesset-still-isnt-functioning/0000018d-5bf2-d0af-a3af-7bfed7db0000</guid></item><item><title>涉嫌参与杀害巴勒斯坦囚犯的五名以色列狱警被转移到其他牢房</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prison-guards-suspected-of-involvement-in-death-of-palestinian-moved-to-other-unit/0000018d-5bd0-d0fc-a9bd-5fdd88750000</link><description>据以色列监狱管理局称，这些看守因一名巴勒斯坦囚犯的死亡而受到警方讯问，这名囚犯被发现有严重暴力的迹象，并被转移到另一个单位，“直到调查完成”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 20:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prison-guards-suspected-of-involvement-in-death-of-palestinian-moved-to-other-unit/0000018d-5bd0-d0fc-a9bd-5fdd88750000</guid></item><item><title>远离加沙，内塔尼亚胡向媒体发起个人战争，提出尖锐问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-30/ty-article/.highlight/far-from-gaza-netanyahu-wages-his-personal-war-on-press-asking-tough-questions/0000018d-5bba-de55-a99d-fffb01db0000</link><description>来自全国各地的人们正在与哈马斯作战，并被哈马斯杀害，因为内塔尼亚胡派他们去那里。其中一些人确实是记者，他们就臃肿的预算和分担草案的负担提出棘手的问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 20:31:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-30/ty-article/.highlight/far-from-gaza-netanyahu-wages-his-personal-war-on-press-asking-tough-questions/0000018d-5bba-de55-a99d-fffb01db0000</guid></item><item><title>新低：以色列主张让加沙人民挨饿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/a-new-low-the-israelis-advocating-to-starve-the-people-of-gaza/0000018d-5b42-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fc0740000</link><description>对于以色列极端分子来说，在加沙，没有什么是禁止的——阻止人道主义援助的运送、重建犹太人定居点、人类尊严。但将它们视为边缘运动是错误的</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 20:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/a-new-low-the-israelis-advocating-to-starve-the-people-of-gaza/0000018d-5b42-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fc0740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队承认淹没加沙哈马斯隧道以摧毁它们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-admits-to-flooding-hamas-tunnels-in-gaza-in-bid-to-destroy-them/0000018d-5b9e-d0af-a3af-7bbec4750000</link><description>以色列迄今为止否认了外国媒体有关在加沙隧道网络中使用洪水系统的报道，现在承认在“合适”的地点使用了这种方法，并且不影响地下水的使用</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 19:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-admits-to-flooding-hamas-tunnels-in-gaza-in-bid-to-destroy-them/0000018d-5b9e-d0af-a3af-7bbec4750000</guid></item></channel></rss>